


Each character will be in one of four leadership categories

Dominant - changes things by overcoming opposition to get results.
Consciousness - Works within existing circumstances to ensure quality and accuracy.
Steadiness- Cooperates with others within existing circumstance to carry out the task. 
Influence - Shapes the environment by influencing or persuading others. 

Each character will be identified based on their name, lead characteristic and sub-class of the lead characteristic
Each lead characteristic will have advantages and disadvantages that will play out on the quest and all of the situations presented
throughout the game. 
